Greek Villages Visualization

manual
-------
* press the same button to deactivate the effect

keys  
 
1 -> view Step By Step(village by village) Greece
2 -> print one Village
3 -> light effect
4 -> print all villages dots
5 -> random list effect
6 -> mouse interaction press mouse to view village
7 -> draw Greece with "0" and "1"
+ -> increase dot radius
- -> reduce dot radius

----------------------------------------
